{"tid":354210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解會有人覺得喺香港地腳踏實地儲錢係可以買到樓?","createTime":"2017-08-10T08:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T12:54:15.000Z","uid":92376,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"82288c4bb9d809bc961b6e42ff6233eaa18a8a38","tid":354210,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:42:28.000Z","msg":"依家個樓市咁撚癲，慳慳埋埋唔知幾耐先有首期，之後又要供幾廿年先供得完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本香港呢個地方唔係比我地正正經經儲錢然後去買樓既地方黎，忠忠直直最後咪渣兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n儲錢既目標係買樓根本不切實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓?依家根本係逼你諗發達，可能中到六合彩先買得起，就算做野係要儲錢，都唔係諗用黎買樓咁白痴囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623d96dd73c4bcb08c686231a55baa2a18e06604","tid":354210,"uid":21306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:19:14.000Z","msg":"同意 而家儲錢都係用黎不時之需 同去旅行<br />\n買樓？無諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夠而家生活就夠了"},{"pid":"ca2fda40a2dc893081b1534e4b967b553840cd2e","tid":354210,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:40:58.000Z","msg":"老實講,我有時係會FF自己如果住大屋點樣,例如咩裝修style<br />\n但從來無諗過係靠做野果啲濕碎錢可以圓到呢個夢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0303e3860c8aa449d0faffa46c8529c868266b7","tid":354210,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:56:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同意 而家儲錢都係用黎不時之需 同去旅行<br />\n買樓？無諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夠而家生活就夠了</bl